trans-unit.source: Represents the abstract base class from which the classes <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData"></xref> and <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey"></xref> derive.
trans-unit.target: Representerer abstrakt basisklasse som klassene <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData"> </xref> og <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey"> </xref> avledet.

trans-unit.source: The EncryptedType class represents the abstract base class from which the classes <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> derive.
trans-unit.target: Klassen EncryptedType representerer abstrakt basisklasse som klassene <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>og <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey>avledet.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>

trans-unit.source: These two classes contain the actual encrypted data or key information in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Disse to klasser som inneholder den faktiske krypterte data eller nøkkelinformasjon i XML-kryptering.

trans-unit.source: To comply with XML encryption standards, you should use these two derived classes.
trans-unit.target: For å overholde XML-krypteringsstandarder, bør du bruke disse to avledede klasser.

trans-unit.source: For more information on XML encryption standards, see http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om XML-krypteringsstandarder, kan du se http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.

trans-unit.source: Adds an <xref uid="langword_csharp_<EncryptionProperty>" name="<EncryptionProperty>" href=""></xref> child element to the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<EncryptedProperties>" name="<EncryptedProperties>" href=""></xref> element in the current <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedType"></xref> object in XML encryption.

trans-unit.source: This method can be used to add `<EncryptionProperty>` child elements to the `<EncryptedProperties>` element.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kan brukes til å legge til `<EncryptionProperty>` underordnede elementer til den `<EncryptedProperties>` elementet.

trans-unit.source: The `<EncryptedProperties>` element provides additional information for the `<EncryptedType>` element.
trans-unit.target: Den `<EncryptedProperties>` elementet gir ekstra informasjon om den `<EncryptedType>` elementet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData"></xref> value for an instance of an <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedType"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData"> </xref> verdien for en forekomst av en <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedType"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The `<CipherData>` element is a required element in XML encryption that provides the encrypted data.
trans-unit.target: Den `<CipherData>` elementet er et nødvendig element i XML-kryptering som inneholder de krypterte dataene.

trans-unit.source: It must either contain the encrypted octet sequence as the base64-encoded text of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherValue%2A> property, or provide a reference to an external location containing the encrypted octet sequence using the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherReference%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Det må inneholde den krypterte oktett sekvensen som base64-kodede teksten i den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherValue%2A>-egenskapen, eller oppgi en referanse til en ekstern plassering som inneholder den krypterte oktett rekkefølge ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherReference%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherReference%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about this element, see <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om dette elementet, kan du se <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData"></xref> object.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Encoding" name="Encoding" href=""></xref> attribute of an <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedType"></xref> instance in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Encoding" name="Encoding" href=""> </xref> for en <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedType"> </xref> forekomst i XML-kryptering.

trans-unit.source: This property describes the encoding of the encrypted data.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen beskriver kodingen for de krypterte dataene.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the encrypted data is a base64-encoded PNG, the encoding could be specified as 'http://www.w3.org/2000/09/xmldsig#base64'.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis de krypterte dataene er en base64-kodede PNG, kan kodingen angis som "http://www.w3.org/2000/09/xmldsig#base64".

trans-unit.source: A string that describes the encoding of the encrypted data.
trans-unit.target: En streng som beskriver kodingen for de krypterte dataene.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<EncryptionMethod>" name="<EncryptionMethod>" href=""></xref> element for XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref uid="langword_csharp_<EncryptionMethod>" name="<EncryptionMethod>" href=""> </xref> elementet for XML-kryptering.

trans-unit.source: The `<EncryptionMethod>` is an optional element that describes the encryption algorithm applied to the encrypted data.
trans-unit.target: Den `<EncryptionMethod>` er et valgfritt element som beskriver krypteringsalgoritmen som ble brukt til de krypterte dataene.

trans-unit.source: If the element is absent, the encryption algorithm must be known by the recipient or decryption will fail.
trans-unit.target: Hvis elementet ikke finnes, krypteringsalgoritmen må være kjent av mottakeren eller dekryptering mislykkes.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod"></xref> object that represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<EncryptionMethod>" name="<EncryptionMethod>" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod"> </xref> objektet som representerer den <xref uid="langword_csharp_<EncryptionMethod>" name="<EncryptionMethod>" href=""> </xref> elementet.

trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref uid="langword_csharp_<EncryptionProperties>" name="<EncryptionProperties>" href=""> </xref> element i XML-kryptering.

trans-unit.source: The `<EncryptionProperties>` element can contain additional information about the creation of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedType> instance, such as a date and time stamp or the serial number of cryptographic hardware used during encryption.
trans-unit.target: Den `<EncryptionProperties>` elementet kan inneholde mer informasjon om oppretting av den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedType>forekomsten, for eksempel en dato- og tidsstempel eller serienummeret for kryptografisk maskinvare som brukes under kryptering.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedType>
